      "content": "hey, i'm working on this paper about AI cognitive limits for a nature submission but im kinda freaking out. the results are super interesting but i only managed to get 10 participants for the pilot phase before the lab closed. \n\nhere's the rough summary: \"test showed that LLMs struggle with spatial reasoning in 8/10 cases when presented with non-euclidean geometry.\"\n\ncan u help me draft a high-impact abstract for this? i really need this to sound convincing enough for top-tier editors despite the small N.",
